---
title: Fragrant Spanish Style Rice with Yellow Pepper, Chicken & Chorizo
description: Requiring minimal effort, but resulting in maximum flavour, our Spanish-style rice takes ‘one pot wonders’ to dizzying new heights. Bursting with deliciously earthy flavours and packed with lots of hidden veggies, this colourful dish will delight even the fussiest of eaters. Place this beautiful pot right in the middle of your dinner table and enjoy in a traditional, communal style. No mealtime meltdowns in sight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fragrant-paella-3468b27d-0d523ea5.jpg
